Requirements:
- Curl
- PHP5+

The actual client is located in lib/blippy.php. The supporting files in ./oauth_example demonstrates a 3-legged OAuth exchange with blippy.
The example OAuth application is already set up with a testing consumer key and secret and callback set to http://localhost. In order to get
this example working, set your apache doc root to oauth_example and verify apache is listening on localhost. 

For support visit http://groups.google.com/group/blippy or #blippy on freenode 

- The Blippy Team
